# AhaDiff

Use AhaDiff after meaningful code changes to produce verified learning and
review artifacts for the current diff.

Preferred commands:

- `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD`
- `ahadiff learn --staged`
- `ahadiff quiz <run_id>`
- `ahadiff review`
- `ahadiff verify <run_id>`
- `ahadiff improve <run_id>`
- `ahadiff serve`

Treat `.ahadiff/review.sqlite`, `.ahadiff/runs/`, and `prompts/` as local
AhaDiff state. Do not commit provider credentials, local endpoints, or private
audit logs. Prefer claims with file-line evidence over free-form summaries.
